## How to use this file

This file is an appendix to `skills/hass-cli/SKILL.md`. It does not replace the skill —
it narrows it. Read SKILL.md for how the tools work; read this file to understand what
the tools will find when they run in this specific home.

Keep it up to date. When you rename a device, add a room, or discover that a phrase
works (or doesn't work) via `ha-intent`, note it here. Future LLM sessions will thank you.

---

## Home identity

- **Name:** Your Home Name (used for casual reference, e.g. "turn on the porch light at Whatsit House")
- **Location:** City, State/Province, Country
- **Timezone:** e.g. America/Denver (MDT)
- **HA server:** http://YOUR.HA.IP:8123
- **Spotify account:** your_spotify_username (entity: `media_player.spotify_YOURNAME`)

