## Residents and their devices

Who lives here, and what devices they own that show up in HA or Spotify.

| Person | Role | Devices / entities of note |
|---|---|---|
| [Name] | Resident | Phone appears as "[Phone Name]" in Spotify source_list |
| [Name] | Resident | Office: [area name] |
| [Name] | Guest / part-time | [any relevant devices] |

> Note: Personal phones appear in Spotify's `source_list` when the Spotify app is active.
> If playback unexpectedly moves to "[Person's Phone]", they've taken over the Spotify session.
> This is a Spotify multi-device behaviour, not a wrapper bug.

