## Known ha-intent phrases

Phrases verified to work via `ha-intent` in this home. These are backed by custom automations
or intent configurations that go beyond what `ha-on`/`ha-off`/`ha-trigger` can reach.

```
ha-intent "PHRASE"   →  what it does
```

| Phrase | What happens | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| "turn off [room]" | Timed automation sequences lights/switches | Preferred over ha-off for this room |
| "good morning" | Morning routine automation | |
| "good night" | Also available via ha-trigger "good night" | |
| "[scene name]" | Activates scene | |

> When adding new phrases: test with `ha-intent "phrase"` and confirm `status: ok` before
> documenting here. If it returns `no_match`, the phrase is not in HA's intent vocabulary.

